description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 7 Advanced Nurse Practitioner&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specialising in Breast, Endocrine and Skin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to appoint an advanced nurse practitioner to join the Breast, Skin and Endocrine Unit at University Hospitals Dorset NHS Foundation Trust( based at Poole Hospital site).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a nurse with proven ability to work autonomously in an advanced practice role, a qualification in Advanced Nurse Partitioning will be essential .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As there is a significant oncology component to the post, previous experience in medical or surgical oncology as well any of the relevant specialties is desirable but not essential, as training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More important in this role will be a nurse who is highly organised, motivated to learn, with excellent communication and team working skills, innovative and above all patient focused.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return, we can offer the right candidate the support of well-established and highly functioning multidisciplinary teams, with opportunities and support for professional development and specialist training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this sounds like the perfect opportunity for you then we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note: if this job requires you to have a DBS check to enable you to properly fulfil the requirements of the job, on appointment you will be required to repay the cost of obtaining a DBS check and this amount will be reclaimed from your salary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 19/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provisional interview date: week commencing 30/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wish to discuss the role further or for an informal visit please do not hesitate to contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Miss Evans Consultant Breast &amp; Endocrine Surgeon on 0300 019 8158 or via Email: Abigail.Evans@uhd.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lucy Merrifield , Acting Matron for Surgery &amp; Gynaecology Email: lucy.merrifield@uhd.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
